The mother is lashing out at VI/EQ because she knows there were things as a parent that she either wasn't doing, or didn't do...or maybe she doesn't know, I sometimes give the human race way too much credit.<br>
<br>
If this person was mentally ill or mentally challenged, either case...for him to be let go into the spin where <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> anything</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> took that much control of his life, then somewhere along the way, someone wasn't looking out for his best interests....<br>
