Maybe she didn't say much about eq, cuz it kept him out of her hair.  Maybe if he wasout of her hair, she didn't have to think about how she apparently fucked up as a parent....or maybe things like that didn't even cross her mind.<br>
<br>
Pardon my ranting, I hadn't realized how strongly I feel about people like this woman.<br>
<br>
She's not mourning her son, she's looking for his deat hnot to be her fault. And I'm not at all saying it is. Suicide is sadly, not always a black and white thing. <br>
<br>
I mean for the average Joe to kill himself over a chick, I think that's lame....but to someone either mentally ill, or mentally challenged, it may be The Worst Thing that's ever happened, because they may not be able to see past the right now.<br>
<br>
